# iOS Simulator Preference

## Simulator

Use **iPhone Air** as the default simulator for running tests and builds.

- **Test:** `portent-ios-test` (from repo root)
- **Build:** `portent-ios-build` (from repo root)

When specifying a destination, prefer `name=iPhone Air` over other simulators for consistency across runs. See root `scripts/portent-aliases.sh` for canonical commands.
